    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1980-02-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1980-02-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="254"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d254">
                <head>254. Memorandum From the President’s Assistant for National Security Affairs
                        (<persName corresp="#p_BZK_1">Brzezinski</persName>) to Secretary of State
                        <persName corresp="#p_VCR_1">Vance</persName>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d254fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Affairs, Brzezinski Material, <persName corresp="#p_BZK_1"
                            >Brzezinski</persName> Office File, Country Chron File, Box 44,
                        Rhodesia: 1980. Confidential.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1980-02-19">February 19, 1980</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>Diplomatic Relations with Zimbabwe</item>
                </list>
                <p>The President has read your memorandum of February 8<note n="2" xml:id="d254fn2"
                        >See <ref target="#d253">Document 253</ref>.</note> on the above subject and
                    approved, in principle, the establishment of diplomatic relations with
                        Zimbabwe,<note n="3" xml:id="d254fn3">The United States established
                        diplomatic relations with Zimbabwe on April 18.</note> with a final decision
                    on implementation to be made following the elections, February 27–29. (C)</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_BZK_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Zbigniew Brzezinski</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
